N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 443.3 - Filing of proposed records units

State Regulations

Every steam corporation affected by this Part shall file on
or before February 1, 1937, a statement setting forth the continuing property
record units proposed to be used in its continuing property
record. Notes
